      • getParentPermissions

        public MemberPermission[] getParentPermissions()
        Returns:
        the member permissions that will be checked along with this operator permission.
        If this is not null (or empty) then before checking the operator permission we'll check if the operator's owner member has at least one of these (related) permissions.
